  "notes": [
    "This study compares GenMine TOP (dual DNA-RNA panel) with FoundationOne CDx (DNA-only panel) for sarcoma genomic profiling using real-world data from Japan's nationwide C-CAT database.",
    "The dual DNA-RNA panel showed superior performance in detecting fusion genes, particularly histology-specific fusions in translocation-related sarcomas.",
    "Germline pathogenic variants were only detectable with the tumor-normal matched GenMine TOP panel, not with the tumor-only FoundationOne CDx panel."
  ]
